race.comment: DANA MAC (2) jumped from this box last time and also the same course and distance when a 4 length third (19.36) in a Grade 5. Rates a top chance. BENNY MOKO (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Dana Curly (19.36) in a Grade 5. Expected to be in the finish again. INDECISION (1) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at this track over 330m behind Scrutinise (19.52) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Leading chance. IRINKA SCOTT (3) is a last-start placegetter at big odds who will have admirers.
